{"tid":1276503,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"71g20過後 新戰線 應該咁打","createTime":"2019-07-02T03:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:00:42.000Z","uid":191392,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c93860760c30ab1c3f31795728a3a40ca0d0d9cc","tid":1276503,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除咗要輿論戰仲有文宣戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港令北京惶恐不安 公安部內部文件流出<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275934</a><br />\n<br />\n今朝睇到呢2個post <br />\n<br />\n上海強推垃圾分類 民怨四起<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275942</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前我亦叫過大家 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好傳野sip 反送中野去蝗到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無奈地小弟太廢 聚唔到人手一齊做 只有自己係 空閒時間做遊擊不停去上水東鐵airdrop 同買張太空卡用wechat send 畀大陸人 <br />\n其餘日子都有一齊同大家發夢<br />\n但71打後好似就無再有可行活動發起<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個係小弟以前建議希望有文宣同傳單組會幫手帶起</span><br />\n<br />\n我個人能力唔夠<br />\n對唔住大家...<br />\n希望有人會帶到上文宣到<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我上一個Post到諗到去羅湖/上水/沙田/落馬洲派反送中傳單畀蝗<br />\n等佢地帶上去蝗國<br />\n多D 蝗知發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n「急」如果係落馬洲羅湖口岸派返以前嘅反送中單張<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1247839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1247839</a><br />\n<br />\n作用：<br />\n1.暫停自由行 光復上水同全香港<br />\n2.消息傳開（中共最驚）<br />\n3.有效過用網絡<br />\n4.證明送中條例，如果派傳單都拉人，送中條例可以帶曬所有人上去了<br />\n5.黑警/公安拉人美帝可以出手<br />\n6. 我地無成本亦唔犯法<br />\n7. 各有各做，和平，唔洗衝，但對港共，中共極有效<br />\n8. 有用過圍堵<br />\n9.勇武和理非都唔會屌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地可以</span><br />\n派反送中傳單，貼貼紙，Airdrop，播黑警片嘅電視<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極力反對各位放傳單入佢地背囊同貼上個GIP到</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時班蝗佢地帶曬上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">一致對外，香港加油</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">尋晚發夢辛苦了 我地場夢仲有好長 唔好放棄 </span></span>"},{"pid":"77bc3d9a617b516c811ec7f83110d7b716dc407b","tid":1276503,"uid":191392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"另外希望大家一齊整長輩圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明日大嶼 國歌法 監控系統</span><br />\n都準備好喇 大家小心<br />\n中環海濱輸咗<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地可以再輸</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長輩圖生成器<br />\n<a href=\"http://files.rei.idv.tw/thumb/older/9b5084f1c33a668c21ee3e0ce7ab8c94.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffiles.rei.idv.tw%2Fthumb%2Folder%2F9b5084f1c33a668c21ee3e0ce7ab8c94.html&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=27db8268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://files.rei.idv.tw/thumb/older/9b5084f1c33a668c21ee3e0ce7ab8c94.html</a>"},{"pid":"2a53e111194342f5986946db5450b8525225ea50","tid":1276503,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:32:18.000Z","msg":"推呀 唔好咁都無人睇呀"},{"pid":"0273af47b3a81f694c6839d0fced7a509d29d2c9","tid":1276503,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50b471444d953e8129d1865e855972ceac225662","tid":1276503,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870dc652a9d14971d99726d9f5f02caf549fe62e","tid":1276503,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9fb6abcb389731273aabeb1073cf78d8a1e40a3","tid":1276503,"uid":180324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ccde7d3178a9615c8a6bff26b90370eed8b4a455","tid":1276503,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c6551a319b58e0e1f6578bfe94f14c2a229a1fee","tid":1276503,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:25:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d4edfce5257c5a156a1e4b9095ec16cd663ced3","tid":1276503,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47f97ffd412a66c3b8b86c2ebe742f619aee4cab","tid":1276503,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67ba133136eae1e4f174311865157186eafc7711","tid":1276503,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}